                    "<p>Whether due to a velstrac's manipulations or a planar jaunt gone horribly wrong, your bloodline was infused with a vein of shadow.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> occult</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Occultism, Stealth</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Void Warp]{Chill Touch}</em>; 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Grim Tendrils]</em>; 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Darkness]</em>; 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Chilling Darkness]</em>; 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Phantasmal Killer]</em>; 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shadow Siphon]</em>; 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Collective Transposition]</em>; 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Duplicate Foe]</em>; 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Disappearance]</em>; 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Weird]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dim the Light]</em>; advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Steal Shadow]</em>; greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Consuming Darkness]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> Shadows grow deeper around you or one target, either granting a +1 status bonus to Stealth or imposing a -1 status penalty to Perception for 1 round.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Shadow Blood Magic (Perception)], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Shadow Blood Magic (Stealth)]</p>",
